wikifunctionsclient-functioncall-error:
Error shown when a wikitext function call goes wrong.

Params:
* $1 - The specific error message

{{Doc-wikilambda}}
wikifunctionsclient-functioncall-error-c:
A [[:mw:Special:MyLanguage/Help:Tracking categories|tracking category]] added to a page with a function call that results in an error. Please don't add namespace prefix.

{{Doc-wikilambda}}

Description of the generic Wikifunctions error tracking category
